
# Azure Cloud Security Projects

This section contains hands-on implementations of security controls in Microsoft Azure environments, demonstrating practical application of cloud security principles.

## Projects Overview

### [Lab 03: Azure Firewall Implementation](./Lab-03-Azure-Firewall/)

Deployed and configured Azure Firewall as a centralised network security control with custom routing and rule-based filtering.

**Key Achievements**:
- Implemented network segmentation with three isolated subnets
- Configured User-Defined Routes to force traffic inspection
- Created FQDN-based application rules for web filtering
- Established protocol-level network rules for DNS resolution
- Validated defense-in-depth security architecture

**Technologies**: Azure Firewall, Virtual Networks, User-Defined Routes, Network Security Groups

---

